  Many believe that there are some of the characteristics a lady should have or portray to show that she is a wife material. Reno Omokri on the other hand has decided to give the list of characteristics he feels a wife material must have. The human rights activist took his time out to list what he believes and many of his fans supported it fully. READ ALSO: Reno Omokri Slams Those Protesting For BBNaija’s Pere Reno who is known for dishing daily advice called nuggets has come out with a new addition to the list as he curates a list of characteristics to look out for in a woman who is intended to be made a wife. Taking to his Instagram page, Reno Omokri wrote; If she has these features, then consider making her your future.”